6b45ee7b1afafe653441edf763a","tid":1450892,"uid":291626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:25:47.000Z","msg":"幫手推阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7334cce04b048a6594e5a56a03a134d195c6506","tid":1450892,"uid":36321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:26:04.000Z","msg":"我教你分別「真抗爭者」同「警察臥底」！<br />\n<br />\n「警察臥底」唔敢掟汽油彈！唔敢掟磚！唔會打警察！<br />\n因為真係傷到差佬，佢出緊咩任務都收唔到科。<br />\n就係咁樣，用行動分，唔好用口號去分～<br />\n<br />\n打警察嘅，就肯定自己人！<br />\n<br />\n大家可以因爲各樣理由，而不去動武，不作激烈行動，這是可以理解的。<br />\n但千萬不可因爲警察有臥底，就趁機跟衝鋒陷陣的行動者割𥱊！將所有行動都講成警察詭計，是對行動者的誣陷，是解散軍所為！"},{"pid":"406fcf21f2cae1b654a7172e462a8cd38478c98f","tid":1450892,"uid":291626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:26:07.000Z","msg":"幫手推阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e582577145497b8657ba883bcb53813e2480258","tid":1450892,"uid":178364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:26:16.000Z","msg":"唔同意要大肆宣傳 又話核彈都唔割？咁做即係否認勇武嘅行動 同割蓆無分別"},{"pid":"5174789682c0698147d9979962770fe4257f498e","tid":1450892,"uid":291626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e582577145497b8657ba883bcb53813e2480258","tid":1450892,"uid":178364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:26:16.000Z","msg":"唔同意要大肆宣傳 又話核彈都唔割？咁做即係否認勇武嘅行動 同割蓆無分別"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:27:37.000Z","msg":"豬阿 可以話係警察一開始就已經做緊戲 引我地升級"},{"pid":"779cd2b9bb15044dff19568b716a41f3e9b807ea","tid":1450892,"uid":291626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0